Supported Hardware:
  Drivers will automatically detect which underlying vendor-provided drivers are
  available.

  Supported:
    Viewpoint
    National Instruments NI-DAQmx
    Marvin Test:
      GxFpga for digital output using AFRL firmware (verified with GX3500)
      GxAo for analog output (not yet complete)
    Comedi
    BeagleBone Black with AFRL firmware/hardware:
      timing using PRU (not yet complete)
      DDS using PRU + AFRL/DDS Cape
